    <section id="about" class="about-section">
        <h2>Smile Airlines</h2>
        <p>Welcome to VAYU Airlines, where your journey is our priority. We are dedicated to providing world-class
            flight services with a focus on safety, comfort, and convenience. Whether you're traveling for business,
            leisure, or any other reason, VAYU ensures a seamless experience from takeoff to landing.</p>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="mission">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>To connect people across the globe with safe, reliable, and affordable air travel, while continuously
                    innovating and improving our services to exceed expectations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="values">
                <h3>Our Values</h3>
